{"tid":1250820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂騎牆派本來就已經唔係企我地個邊","createTime":"2019-06-22T08:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T08:34:10.000Z","uid":260037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8aee37661f879233de545cf553d87c2987f122","tid":1250820,"uid":260037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"純發洩<br />\n<br />\n拎蛇齋餅糉班廢佬夠係騎牆派啦<br />\n咪又係睇利益黎投獻世派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個啲所謂 搖擺民意 根本就唔牢固 <br />\n唔係最堅實嘅抗爭基礎<br />\n<br />\n真正支持嘅人 可能會唔理解點解要咁做<br />\n但絕對唔會因為咁就企係警狗個邊<br />\n<br />\n話人地浪費食物就轉立場個班<br />\n屌你老母啦 平時清潔啊姐抹你啲屎屎尿尿又唔見你話辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過呢幾日受到cctvb煽動 好多和理非都可能會屌幾句 但香港人咁撚善忘 <br />\n我地文宣努力多啲 keep住真正嘅支持者就夠<br />\n<br />\nbtw 大家真係每一次都進步緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要繼續一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}